   PHPPO's network of distance learning projects.
   SMDP - Sustainable Management Development Program
   PHPPO's global health training program.
   NLTN - National Laboratory Training Network
   The NLTN is a training system sponsored by the Association of Public
   Health Laboratories (APHL) and the Centers for Disease Control and
   Prevention (CDC).
